I know, it's been two years since my last update due to the fact that I have ignored this project for some time now. 

Changes since 0.8:
- Added back alley area.
- Added extra room + vent underground.
- Added a way into one of the buildings.
- Added a way into the house in front of the CT spawn.
- Expanded area in front of T spawn.
- Removed existing vent system.
- Plus some other minor changes.
